---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div id="different">
  <Container>
    <div class="md:w-2/3">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="currentColor"
        class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary"
      >
        <path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813A3.75 3.75 0 007.466 7.89l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5zM18 1.5a.75.75 0 01.728.568l.258 1.036c.236.94.97 1.674 1.91 1.91l1.036.258a.75.75 0 010 1.456l-1.036.258c-.94.236-1.674.97-1.91 1.91l-.258 1.036a.75.75 0 01-1.456 0l-.258-1.036a2.625 2.625 0 00-1.91-1.91l-1.036-.258a.75.75 0 010-1.456l1.036-.258a2.625 2.625 0 001.91-1.91l.258-1.036A.75.75 0 0118 1.5zM16.5 15a.75.75 0 01.712.513l.394 1.183c.15.447.5.799.948.948l1.183.395a.75.75 0 010 1.422l-1.183.395c-.447.15-.799.5-.948.948l-.395 1.183a.75.75 0 01-1.422 0l-.395-1.183a1.5 1.5 0 00-.948-.948l-1.183-.395a.75.75 0 010-1.422l1.183-.395c.447-.15.799-.5.948-.948l.395-1.183A.75.75 0 0116.5 15z"
          clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
      </svg>

      <h2
        class="my-5 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-6xl"
      >
        What makes us different
        <!-- A technology-first approach to chronic disease management -->
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg">
        We use technology to address chronic disease management, allowing for
        continuous real-time health monitoring, data analysis for pattern
        detection, trend prediction, and the provision of immediate,
        personalized care, making care plans more efficient and effective.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-2"
    >
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative space-y-4 py-6 p-8">
          <div class="flex space-y-2 items-center">
            <img
              src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341139.png"
              class="w-10"
              width="200"
              height="200"
              alt="burger illustration"
            />
            <h5
              class="ml-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Sustainable Healthcare
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-8 text-lg">
            DiaBeatIt revolutionizes chronic disease management by reversing the
            traditional healthcare model. Instead of patients needing to travel
            to see their doctors, DiaBeatIt brings the doctor's expertise
            directly to the patients. The subscription-based model enables a
            sustainable approach to managing chronic diseases like diabetes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative space-y-4 py-6 p-8">
          <div class="flex space-y-2 items-center">
            <img
              src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341025.png"
              class="w-12"
              width="512"
              height="512"
              alt="burger illustration"
            />
            <h5
              class="ml-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Timely Interventions
            </h5>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-8 text-lg">
              DiaBeatIt's system enables timely interventions for chronic
              disease management. It continuously monitors patients' health
              metrics, facilitating preventive care by detecting abnormal trends
              early, allowing doctors to intervene before a situation becomes
              critical. Moreover, the system immediately alerts doctors when it
              detects any abnormalities, enabling a quick response.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div class="relative space-y-4 py-12 p-8">
          <div class="flex space-y-2 items-center">
            <img
              src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341160.png"
              class="w-12"
              width="512"
              height="512"
              alt="burger illustration"
            />
            <h5
              class="ml-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Patient Centric
            </h5>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-8 text-lg">
              DiaBeatIt's patient-centric approach emphasizes active monitoring
              and personalized medical support. Patients use Continuous Glucose
              Monitoring devices for diabetes tracking, promoting personal
              involvement in their care. The system enables personalized medical
              support by allowing healthcare providers to analyze patients'
              health data and tailor treatment accordingly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
      >
        <div
          class="relative space-y-4 py-12 p-8 transition duration-300 group-hover:bg-white dark:group-hover:bg-gray-800"
        >
          <div class="flex space-y-2 items-center">
            <img
              src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341134.png"
              class="w-12"
              width="512"
              height="512"
              alt="burger illustration"
            />
            <h5
              class="ml-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
            >
              Adaptability & Scalability
            </h5>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-8 text-lg">
              DiaBeatIt's system is both adaptable and scalable, making it a
              sustainable tool for managing various chronic diseases. Its
              functions can be tailored to monitor different health metrics for
              specific conditions, and the system can expand to accommodate more
              patients and diseases. Additionally, it's designed to integrate
              new health data as medical technology evolves, ensuring its
              relevance and value over time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
